#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn51.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn51.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn51.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Cāpālavagga "
msgstr "1. At the Cāpāla Shrine "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn51.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Ariyasutta "
msgstr "3. A Noble One "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn51.3:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, iddhipādā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ariyā niyyānikā niyyanti takkarassa sammā dukkhakkhayāya. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when these four bases of psychic power are developed and cultivated they are noble and emancipating, and bring one who practices them to the complete ending of suffering. "

msgctxt "sn51.3:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn51.3:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to enthusiasm … "

msgctxt "sn51.3:1.4"
msgid "vīriyasamādhi … pe … "
msgstr "energy … "

msgctxt "sn51.3:1.5"
msgid "cittasamādhi … pe … "
msgstr "mental development … "

msgctxt "sn51.3:1.6"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti. "
msgstr "inquiry, and active effort. "

msgctxt "sn51.3:1.7"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro iddhipādā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ariyā niyyānikā niyyanti takkarassa sammā dukkhakkhayāyā”ti. "
msgstr "When these four bases of psychic power are developed and cultivated they are noble and emancipating, and bring one who practices them to the complete ending of suffering.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.3:1.8"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
